1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 12:04:50\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 12:04:50\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:783:\"There is an opportunity for a Qualified Staff Nurse with two years post qualifying experience to join a busy and dynamic department.\r\nYou will be expected to admit and discharge surgical patients following strict criteria. Therefore potential candidates must be able to demonstrate a high level of knowledge of surgical procedures. An ability to problem solve is essential.\r\nStaff nurses must be able to evidence continual professional development and be undertaking education at degree level. Mentoring students and newly qualified staff requires the successful candidate to have a Mentoring Qualification.\r\nPaediatric experience is desirable. However there will be an opportunity to gain paediatric skills. You will be expected to attend PILS and ILS as a Day Surgery Practitioner.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:37:\"Senior Staff Nurse - Day Surgery Unit\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:48:\"contact-us-3-senior-staff-nurse-day-surgery-unit\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2016-02-20 11:07:22\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-02-20 11:07:22\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:80:\"http://eburtonservices.com/job/contact-us-3-senior-staff-nurse-day-surgery-unit/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:2283;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 12:01:11\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 12:01:11\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:605:\"A Renal Unit in Jersey requires an experienced nurse manager to provide leadership and management of a team of experienced renal nurse specialists.\r\n\r\nThe successful candidate will be a registered nurse with 5 years post qualifying experience, 3 years experience in the specialism, educated to 1st Degree equivalent with a management or leadership award and following a post graduate study pathway.\r\n\r\nA proven track record of successfully implementing and managing change is essential. Developing services that put patient’s safety, quality and patient experience at the heart of everything they do.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:26:\"Senior Sister - Renal Unit\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:37:\"contact-us-3-senior-sister-renal-unit\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2016-02-20 11:20:40\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-02-20 11:20:40\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:69:\"http://eburtonservices.com/job/contact-us-3-senior-sister-renal-unit/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:2280;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 11:46:16\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 11:46:16\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:597:\"We are seeking a self motivated and enthusiastic individual to join our client\'s busy team with the key responsibility of providing a social work perspective.\r\n\r\nThe successful candidate will be an experienced Social Worker with recent Children\'s service experience and additional post qualification education.\r\n\r\nThis is an exciting time to join the service which is growing to better meet the needs of the local community. The Social work role is a key component of the service to ensure that safeguarding is fully embedded and that social and family perspectives effectively influence our work.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:31:\"Senior Social Work Practitioner\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:44:\"contact-us-3-senior-social-work-practitioner\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2016-02-27 19:26:12\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-02-27 19:26:12\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:76:\"http://eburtonservices.com/job/contact-us-3-senior-social-work-practitioner/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:3;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:2257;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 10:02:04\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-01-06 10:02:04\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:310:\"The role will be on an ad hoc basis to maintain service delivery during staff absences. The post holder will work as part of a multi-professional team delivering patient care, under the direction of the Registered Nurse. Please note a police check will be required for this post. Full uniform will be provided.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:35:\"Bank Health Care Assistant - Band 2\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:46:\"contact-us-5-bank-health-care-assistant-band-2\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2016-02-27 20:07:01\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2016-02-27 20:07:01\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:78:\"http://eburtonservi